metadata.name: WAGMI #1
metadata.description:
WAGMI NFTs is so much more than just an homage to the BAYC. WAGMI are a rapid deflationary token that double up as a raffle entry to win one of 6 MAYC giveaways! They are raffle tickets that can grant you access to the most elite club in the NFT space- the Bored Ape Yacht Club community. If you decide to burn your WAGMI ape, you will receive 10x the raffle tickets to win the next prize giveaway.  However, that will be where that WAGMI ape's journey ends. Burnt WAGMI apes will only be valid for the next raffle entry and then go out of circulation, reducing the total supply.

When will you burn your WAGMI?  When will others?  Time it right to maximise your chance of winning.
